                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2002-12-31</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>The text of the book is good and gives some very good advice about programming. But it is important to realize that they are only suggestions, and should sometimes be disregarded.</span>
                  
              
